title: John Hill Brinton's notes on cases : 1861.
note_text: Includes fragmentary manuscript notes of about fifty casualities under Brinton's care in 1861; his sketches of wounds are included. Pages 1-56 are hand-numbered and preceded by a table of contents. Cushing manuscript #16.

title: Masālik al-mamālik, [19th century].
note_text: Liber climatum auctore scheicho Abu-Ishako el-Faresi vulgo el-Issthachri. Ad similitudinem codicis Gothani (= Pertsch 1521) accuratissime delineandum et lapidibus exprimendum curavit Dr. J. H. Moeller. Praemissa est dissertatio de Libri climatum indole, auctore et aetate. Gothae, In libraria Beckeriana, 1839.

title: 880-03 Aṭbāq al-dhahab / Sharaf al-Dīn ʻAbd al-Muʼmin ibn Hibat Allāh al-Maghribī al-Iṣfahānī.
note_text: Incipit of Aṭbāq al-dhahab: "Bismillāh al-Raḥmān al-Raḥīm wa-bi-hi thiqatī. Allāhumma innā naḥmaduka ʻalá mā asbalta min shaʼābīb karamik wa-sabbalta min jalābīb niʻamik wa-nashkuruka ʻalá mā afadta min kalimātika al-tāmmah wa-afdta min hibātika al-ʻāmmah wa-afḍta min ladhādhāt maʻrifatika wa-nafaḍta min radhādhāt ʻārifatika wa-nuthnī ʻalayka bi-mā asalta min ḍaḥḍāḥ al-ʻulūm wa-ghasalta ʻannā min awḍāḥ al-luʼm wa-kaḥaltanā bi-burūd yaqīnika wa-naḥaltanā min jūd yamīnika shukran yamlaʼu khāṣirat al-majhūd wa-ḥamdan yalīqu bi-al-ḥāmid dūna al-maḥmūd ..."

title: 880-03 Aṭbāq al-dhahab / Sharaf al-Dīn ʻAbd al-Muʼmin ibn Hibat Allāh al-Maghribī al-Iṣfahānī.
note_text: Incipit of Aṭwāq al-dhahab fī al-mawāʻiẓ wa-al-khuṭab: "Bismillāh al-Raḥmān al-Raḥīm. Allāhumma innī aḥmaduka ʻalá mā anzalta ilayya min niʻmatik wa-mā azalta ʻannī min niqmatik ʻalá annī lam akun ahlan lil-ūlá wa-kuntu bi-al-thāniyah awlá lawlā faḍlun minka sābiq ḥamd al-ḥāmid warāʼahu yuqṭaf wa-in aʻnaqa fa-ka-annahu maṣfūd yursaf ..."
